[Unit]
Description=Speed Sign Python Service
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStartPre=/bin/sleep 10
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /home/tedes/speedsign.py
WorkingDirectory=/home/tedes
Restart=always
User=root

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target


---------------------------------------

Langkah instalasi

Buat file service:

sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/speedsign.service


Paste isi di atas (ganti nama_script.py sesuai nama file Python kamu).

Simpan lalu reload systemd:

sudo systemctl daemon-reload


Aktifkan supaya otomatis saat boot:

sudo systemctl enable speedsign.service

nonaktif:
sudo systemctl disable speedsign.service


Jalankan manual untuk uji coba:

sudo systemctl start speedsign.service

MEnghentikan service:
sudo systemctl stop speedsign.service



Cek status:

sudo systemctl status speedsign.service


Lihat log realtime:

journalctl -u speedsign.service -f
